OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,GIs broadcast news facing an
OL,7,Gexistential threat? It's a complex `
OL,8,Gand potentially terrifying ` issue.
OL,10,FThe BBC's chief international
OL,11,Fcorrespondent Lyse Doucet reflected
OL,12,Fon the issue at a recent Royal
OL,13,FTelevision Society event.
OL,15,FYou can read a full account of her
OL,16,Fspeech in the current edition of
OL,17,FTelevision magazine on the RTS
OL,18,Fwebsite.
