OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FIt is all too easy for anyone to be
OL,7,Ftaken in by this poison.
OL,9,FAnd this is where I would argue
OL,10,Fmainstream broadcast news has a vital
OL,11,Fpart to play.
OL,13,FThink of the main news programmes on
OL,14,Fthe public service channels as simple
OL,15,Ftrusted sources of information.
OL,17,FIf they get something wrong or an
OL,18,Findividual item falls short of
OL,19,Faccepted standards, there are
OL,20,Fconsequences.
OL,26,@kD@OOUkD@^O]
