OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FIs it time to build on the BBC's
OL,7,Frecent "Trust is Earned" campaign to
OL,8,Fmarket individual programmes?
OL,10,FShould public service broadcasters
OL,11,Fwork together to help the public
OL,12,Funderstand the basics of what they do
OL,13,Fand why?
OL,15,FBut perhaps there might be glimmers
OL,16,Fof hope.
OL,18,FTV news ratings have fallen in recent
OL,19,Fyears. Apart from the more disturbing
OL,20,Freasons I mentioned, some of this is
OL,21,Fsimply down to multichannel TV and
OL,22,Fthe popularity of streaming.
