OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FThe days of Neighbours boosting the
OL,7,Fratings of the One and Six o'Clock
OL,8,FNews seem like something from a
OL,9,Fdistant age.
OL,11,FBut ratings do seem to be
OL,12,Fstabilising. Last Monday the 6.30pm
OL,13,Fregional programmes on BBC One had 4m
OL,14,Fviewers ` the highest ratings of the
OL,15,Fday.
OL,17,FThe clocks went back last night, the
OL,18,Fnights are drawing in and the weather
OL,19,Fis getting worse.
