OL,3,CThe impact of "news avoidance" on
OL,4,Cbroadcast news
OL,6,FTrends are not inevitable ` just as
OL,7,Fthe resurgence of vinyl records and
OL,8,Fthe increase in the use of cash took
OL,9,Fmany by surprise.
OL,11,FThere are many who do not engage with
OL,12,Fbroadcast news and it is important
OL,13,Ffor reputable journalists to try to
OL,14,Freach the public on a whole range of
OL,15,Fplatforms.
OL,17,FBut perhaps reports of its impending
OL,18,Fdemise are, in part, wishful thinking
OL,19,Fby those who might see benefit for
OL,20,Fthemselves in a failure to offer
OL,21,Ffair, balanced and objective news.
